data.description: This Cozy Townhome is located in the city of Stone Mountain. This End Unit comes with plenty of space in each bedroom. Also, there is an Open Concept Dining Room/ Family Room area with a Family Room view from the Kitchen. Relax on the back Patio or observe nature from the side porch. Minutes away from shopping, entertainment, and public transportation. Make this your forever home or investment!
